ontent/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿姆、大肖恩和 Babytron。图片来源：Aaron J. Thornton 和 Barry Brecheisen，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Eminem-Big-Sean-and-Babytron.-Credit-Aaron-J.-Thornton-and-Barry-Brecheisen-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Eminem">阿姆</a>与 Babytron 和<a href="/artists/Big-Sean">Big Sean</a>合作创作了他的全新单曲“Tobey”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/eminem-vs-everyone-comprehensive-list-slim-shady-lyrical-feuds-beefs-2561575"><b>阿姆 vs 所有人：斯利姆·谢迪 (Slim Shady) 的抒情争斗的大量列表</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>《托比》借鉴了传奇超级英雄<em>蜘蛛侠</em>和 2002 年的同名电影，在歌曲的第三节中看到了底特律说唱歌手的蜡像： <em>“托比·马奎尔被蜘蛛咬了，但看，我，那是一只山羊”</em>在说唱之前：“<em>太疯狂了，Shady 走了，但是嘿，也许，我是山羊/与 Big Sean 和 BabyTron 一起，这就是为什么他们如此。”</em></p><p>该单曲的封面艺术由阿姆与底特律说唱歌手大肖恩和 Babytron 一起重现了病毒式的三蜘蛛侠互相指指点点的表情包。这首歌是“Just Loose It”说唱歌手即将发行的第 12 张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-announces-new-album-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-3750971">The Death of Slim Shady (Coup De Grâce)</a> ”中发行的第二首单曲。它遵循主打单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-references-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-incident-on-new-song-houdini-3761145">Houdini</a> ”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="阿姆 - 托比（壮举。Big Sean &amp; Babytron）[官方音频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9xn0OHEZZ8Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>托比的伴奏音乐视频由科尔·贝内特 (Cole Bennett) 执导，将于本周五（7 月 5 日）发布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-drops-trailer-teasing-new-single-tobey-featuring-big-sean-babytron-3770529">此前阿姆曾在社交媒体上调侃过</a>。在视频中，埃米纳姆戴着杰森·沃希斯面具，转动着电锯，鲜血喷涌而出，将一具尸体切开，而巴比特隆和大肖恩在一旁观看。</p><p>这首单曲是埃米纳姆与 BabyTron 的首次合作，也是他与 Big Sean 的第四次合作——他们曾合作创作过歌曲《No Favors》、《Friday Night Cypher》和《Detroit Vs.》。每个人都过去了。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C8xgHEavWo5/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px